    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1939-10-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1939-10-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="736"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d736">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.3331/283c: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Uruguay</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="16" xml:id="d736fn16">Mr. Wilson was en route to his post
                        aboard the S. S. <hi rend="italic">Uruguay</hi>.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-10-21">October 21,
                            1939</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Notice of intention to negotiate a trade agreement with Uruguay was issued here
                        today<note n="17" xml:id="d736fn17">Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                            >Bulletin</hi>, October 21, 1939, p. 418.</note> and the Legation at
                    Montevideo is being instructed to initiate general provisions discussions with
                    the Uruguayan officials at once. You will probably wish to discuss this matter
                    fully with Fowler as the Embassy at Buenos Aires is being instructed to have him
                    assist the Legation in such discussions to the extent permitted by the work in
                    Buenos Aires.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cordell Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
